Job Description
One of our client - a leading engineering, design and consultancy company founded in Europe over 60 years ago. They employ more than 9000 engineers across 200 offices in 20 countries including Northern Europe, India and the Middle East. They pride themselves in emphasizing local experience combined with a global knowledge-base, constantly striving to achieve inspiring and exacting solutions that make a genuine difference to their Clients, end-users and society as a whole.
IPS has been requested to seek a Sr. Process Engineer for there client who will work as a client side in Dragon Oil based in Dubai for 1 year
contract. After the contract with Dragon Oil you will be transferred and will work in Abu Dhabi head office. The scope of the is overseeing the project of Dragon Oil (Turkmenistan Operations) that will partake in a series of modification and upgrades, process optimization and reliability on existing oil and gas production and processing facilities, on behalf of client the engineer will review, comment on the design engineering deliverables of various contractors.
